# Pedal the Harbour

A modern, desktop-first interactive digital guidebook:
**“Pedal the Harbour: A One-Day Sustainable Cycling Guide from Tai Wai to Tai Po Waterfront in Hong Kong.”**

It includes an interactive route map, timeline-style stop panel, rentals/food/tips sections, and a carbon calculator (cycling vs driving).

## Run locally
```bash
python3 -m http.server 8000

