# Contributing

Thanks for your interest in improving Pedal the Harbour.

## Ways to contribute
- Report a bug (screenshots help)
- Suggest content improvements (stops, tips, safety, sustainability)
- Improve design/accessibility/performance
- Add more stops or better route accuracy

## How to propose changes
1. Fork the repository
2. Create a new branch (e.g. `feature/better-stops`)
3. Make changes
4. Open a Pull Request (PR) with a short description and screenshots if UI changed

## Style notes
- Keep the UI minimal and accessible
- Prefer small, readable JS functions
- Avoid adding heavy dependencies unless necessary
